SEG_SUB_V2_3_CalculatedRoute.name: SEG_SUB_V2_3_CalculatedRoute
SEG_SUB_V2_3_CalculatedRoute.desc: Information for Calculated Route: MPP/On Route/Off Route(Recalculating Route).-MPP: Predicted Route(Not the Link from Searched Route). Used if users don.t set Destination. Used with Current Link Information..-On Route: Link from Searched Route. Used with Current Link Information..-Off Route: Used when trying to enter the Rest Area. 'SEG_CalculatedRoute', 'SEG_FormOfWay' and 'SEG_FunctionalRoadClass' are used together. But if it is impossible to decide values of 'SEG_FormOfWay' and 'SEG_FunctionalRoadClass', transmitt Unknown Value. If additional Information happens in forward unit distance, retransmitt it by Event.

Used if users don.t set Destination. Used with Current Link Information..-On Route: Link from Searched Route. Used with Current Link Information..-Off Route: Used when trying to enter the Rest Area. 'SEG_CalculatedRoute', 'SEG_FormOfWay' and 'SEG_FunctionalRoadClass' are used together. But if it is impossible to decide values of 'SEG_FormOfWay' and 'SEG_FunctionalRoadClass', transmitt Unknown Value. If additional Information happens in forward unit distance, retransmitt it by Event.

ENG_IsgEquipped.name: ENG_IsgEquipped
ENG_IsgEquipped.desc: Information if ISG is equipped or not

valueDescAry.enum_0: ISG is not operating Normal engine operating without ISG
valueDescAry.enum_1: Idle stop is activated Idle is stopped by ECU during driving
valueDescAry.enum_2: Automatically started by ECU Engine is automatically started by ECU regardless driver’s volition during idle stop because the condition that ISG function to be prohibited is satisfied, for example SOC is too low.
valueDescAry.enum_3: ISG is prohibited Driver prohibits to activate ISG in order to avoid start lag when he met traffic jam for example.
valueDescAry.enum_4: Fault  existing in ISG. Idle stop is prohibited and engine started automatically if it is idle stop condition.
valueDescAry.enum_5: Idle stop is inhibited by system automatically for safety and  convenient condition related with battery SOC, brake vacuum pressure etc. ISG function check for EOL.
valueDescAry.enum_6: Auto start is deactivated system automatically to keep safety, Such as door open, hood open and seat belt unlock.
valueDescAry.enum_7: If driver shift gear N to D range without braking to make auto starting. (Economy ISG Only)
